{"tid":1702821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一張圖話你聽今次罷工宣傳既力度","createTime":"2019-11-10T02:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T04:02:53.000Z","uid":160887,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4816aea4249154e149a73187487ed73d82e0c602","tid":1702821,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2ssFut.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2ssFut.png&h=443fa9c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n雖然張圖淨係計到去11.7 <br />\n但比起8.5同期都未免差太多<br />\n今日開花最後機會加大力度宣傳罷工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終有心理準備被罷工同冇心理準備差好遠<br />\n<br />\n同埋強制罷工攻略都好少<br />\n唔係話要講到好詳細預約被捕<br />\n但係咁少post討論聽日實好多手足出到黎唔知要做咩"},{"pid":"1d5052bd880cd8e43d2064a723cab3ae932cd62c","tid":1702821,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803f5ce482421685feeb8126947aeca10b7a398f","tid":1702821,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720a02150be000cff1feeaaf3955328e3a9cff4a","tid":1702821,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288da88db47dacad7512eb3276981e2da43d1fcf","tid":1702821,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"efd4792ca147d58a8b64a2c853612bb297ee7c57","tid":1702821,"uid":198214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf40a0f7060582703c6e9da6d497eef98880bc29","tid":1702821,"uid":74155,"lik